<section class="sh-section sh-bleed">
  <div class="sh-container">
    <div class="sh-center"><div class="sh-eyebrow">System logic</div><h2 class="sh-h2">When the concern is complex, the routine should be coordinated.</h2><p class="sh-body" style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;">Many skincare routines are built by stacking products. But stacking is not the same as sequencing.</p></div>
    <div class="comparison" style="margin-top:34px;">
