      <div class="comparison-card good"><h3 class="sh-h3">Shadeless sequence</h3><ul class="sh-list"><li>Step 1 prepares</li><li>Step 2 optimizes</li><li>Step 3 enhances</li><li>One clear system</li><li>Routine logic built in</li></ul></div>
    </div>
    <div class="quote-band">Most routines stack. Shadeless sequences.</div>
  </div>
</section>
